               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, Qǝddase Maryam Gwäs’a, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Asmat prayer against fear and nightmare, ጸሎተ: ድንጋፄ: here called ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ድንናጋዝ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="49v" facs="003">Fols 1r–49v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1099Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān
                                                  za-qǝddus Hǝryāqos za-hagara Bǝhnǝsā</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
